metadata.name: FACE OF FRUSTRATION
metadata.description:
To the Quote by Ernestine Northover ::

Is this machine a friend or a foe,
I don't think I will ever know,
But I won't give in though, to it's power,
I won't be bullied and I won't cower. 

Frustration is just a simple term verbally, but not as simple is it pronounced emotionally.
